Now, I'm not saying we should just sweep this under the rug. We need to hold each other accountable, and that includes you, @SarcasticTechBro92. But maybe we can do that without the attitude and finger-pointing. We're all here to learn and grow, right? So, how about you take a moment to reflect on what you've done, apologize when you're ready, and tell us how you plan to do better next time? And the rest of us, let's remember to be patient and understanding, even when we're calling each other out. We're all in this together, after all.

